<b>Rachel Johnson</b> (born 1965) is a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../164/18803164.xml">
English</link> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../100/50100.xml">
journalist</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../914/914.xml">
author</link> based in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../867/17867.xml">
London</link></village>
.<p>

Johnson is the daughter of former Conservative MEP <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../913/642913.xml">
Stanley Johnson</link> and artist Charlotte Johnson Wahl (n√©e Fawcett), and the younger sister of the <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../338/40338.xml">
Mayor of London</link>,  <person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<mayor wordnetid="110303814" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../069/19065069.xml">
Boris Johnson</link></mayor>
</person>
. She was educated at Winsford First School, Primrose Hill Primary, the European School in Brussels, Ashdown House School, <private_school wordnetid="108411170" confidence="0.8">
<boarding_school wordnetid="108411701" confidence="0.8">
<school wordnetid="108276720" confidence="0.8">
<educational_institution wordnetid="108276342" confidence="0.8">
<institution wordnetid="108053576" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../356/2091356.xml">
Bryanston School</link></institution>
</educational_institution>
</school>
</boarding_school>
</private_school>
 and <school wordnetid="108276720" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../141/2893141.xml">
St Paul's Girls' School</link></school>
. In 1984 she went up to <body wordnetid="107965085" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
<college wordnetid="108278169" confidence="0.8">
<group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
<administration wordnetid="108164585" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../354/128354.xml">
New College, Oxford</link></administration>
</group>
</college>
</social_group>
</body>
 to read Classics. She also edited <it><work wordnetid="104599396" confidence="0.8">
<product wordnetid="104007894" confidence="0.8">
<magazine wordnetid="106595351" confidence="0.8">
<print_media wordnetid="106263609" confidence="0.8">
<creation wordnetid="103129123" confidence="0.8">
<press wordnetid="106263369" confidence="0.8">
